    "-DLL_RELEASE=1 -D_SECURE_SCL=0 -DLL_SEND_CRASH_REPORTS=0 -DNDEBUG -DLL_RELEASE_WITH_DEBUG_INFO=1")

# Don't bother with a MinSizeRel build.

